pulsate.translation[0].definitions[0].de: to make sounds or movements that are strong and regular like a heart beating
pulsate.translation[0].definitions[0].ex: I could see the veins in his neck pulsating.
pulsate.translation[0].definitions[1].de: to be strongly affected by a powerful emotion or feeling
